{{zh-forms|[[此地无银三百两]]|[[此地]][[無]][[銀]][[三]][[百]][[兩]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: cĭdì wú yín sān băi liăng
===Etymology===
Literally: No 300 [[w:tael|tael]]s of silver buried here.
===Idiom===
# a clumsy denial resulting in self-exposure; a very poor lie which reveals the truth; protest one's innocence too much

